  • Classes in com.datumbox.common.objecttypes used by com.datumbox.applications.datamodeling 
    Class and Description
    Learnable
    This interface is used to mark classes which store parameters that are learned during training.
    Parameterizable
    This interface is used to mark classes that work as wrappers/containers of fields that parameterize other algorithms.
    Trainable
    This interface is used to mark classes that can be trained.
